      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:21:1",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) حَدُّ اللُّوطِيِّ مِثْلُ حَدِّ الزَّانِي وَ قَالَ إِنْ كَانَ قَدْ أُحْصِنَ رُجِمَ وَ إِلَّا جُلِدَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahi, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, from Muhammad Bin Sinan, from Al A’ala Bin Al Fazeyl who said, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) of the sodomist is like the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) of the adulterer’. And he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘If he was married, would be stoned, or else whipped’."
        ]
      }
